OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FGlasgow is Scotland's "most generous
OL,8,Fcity", with donations to Sir Chris
OL,9,FHoy's charity cycling appeal helping
OL,10,Fit claim the title, according to
OL,11,Fcrowdfunding platform GoFundMe.
OL,13,FThe fundraising company compared per
OL,14,Fcapita donations throughout 2025 on
OL,15,Fits online service.
OL,17,FLiverpool emerged as the "most
OL,18,Fgenerous" in the UK, with Glasgow
OL,19,Ftaking second place.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@EO]yD@ZOUzD@IO]
