OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772071403
OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FEdinburgh was Scotland's second-most
OL,8,Fgenerous city and ranked tenth in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FGlasgow's position comes after a
OL,12,Fsizeable response to Sir Chris' Tour
OL,13,Fde 4 cycling challenge, which raised
OL,14,Fmore than #3.1 million in its
OL,15,Finaugural year in 2025.
OL,17,FThe Olympic star, who is battling
OL,18,Fstage four cancer, is launching the
OL,19,Fchallenge again this year and the 2026
OL,20,Ffundraising will support five major UK
OL,21,Fcancer charities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
