OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772071403
OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe date of last year's Tour de 4,
OL,8,FSeptember 7, saw the most donations in
OL,9,FGlasgow and Scotland.
OL,11,FThe largest single funding campaign in
OL,12,FScotland involved #184,000 being
OL,13,Fraised for the family of Rangers fan
OL,14,FChristopher Potter.
OL,16,FHe was killed after being struck by
OL,17,Ftwo cars in Istanbul while following
OL,18,Fthe team. It included a donation from
OL,19,Fformer Scotland star Robert Snodgrass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
