FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772071403
OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FGoFundMe chief executive Tim Cadogan
OL,8,Fpresented the Lord Provost with an
OL,9,Faward to mark Glasgow's generosity.
OL,11,FHe said: "Glasgow's achievement in
OL,12,Fbecoming the most generous city in
OL,13,FScotland and second most generous in
OL,14,Fthe UK is a testament to its long
OL,15,Ftradition of solidarity and compassion.
OL,17,F"Tour de 4 encapsulates this kindness
OL,18,Fin physical form ` people from all
OL,19,Fover the world coming together in
OL,20,FGlasgow to help each other."
OL,26,@sD@JOUyD@AOU|D@\O]
