OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772071403
OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FLord Provost of Glasgow, Jacqueline
OL,8,FMcLaren, said: "I am delighted to
OL,9,Faccept this award on behalf of the
OL,10,Fpeople of Glasgow.
OL,12,F"This recognition from GoFundMe
OL,13,Freflects something that we already
OL,14,Fknow to be true; kindness and
OL,15,Fgenerosity is woven into the very
OL,16,Ffabric of our city.
OL,26,@pD@POUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
