OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772071403
OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,F"Whether responding to moments of
OL,8,Fcrisis and hardship, supporting local
OL,9,Fcauses, or getting behind challenges
OL,10,Flike the Tour de 4, Glaswegians
OL,11,Fconsistently step forward for one
OL,12,Fanother.
OL,14,F"Being acknowledged as Scotland's most
OL,15,Fgenerous city, in addition to once
OL,16,Fagain being named the UK's
OL,17,Ffriendliest, speaks volumes about the
OL,18,Ftype of city we are.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
