OL,3,CGlasgow named Scotland's 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous city' after response to Hoy
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,F"I am proud of everyone who
OL,8,Fcontributed to this achievement, and I
OL,9,Fknow Glasgow will continue to lead
OL,10,Fwith humanity in the year ahead."
